::Cledar/Forrior/Blyer/Firearm/Rixer/Prowl/Cyndro::

Cledar sighs in relief when he hears the reply.

"Oh good. Ok, can I register three bots? Names are Cledar, Forrior, and Blyer."

He heast Firearm approaching, and adds to his transmission: "Make that four. Forth one is Firearm. We're all Maximals"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Rixer reaches Maximal City, walking up to make sure that the shields wern't on.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Prowl exits Maximal City, looking up at the craft Devil Gigatron was in and then looking around for IR.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Cyndro hears Devil Gigatron arrive, and detects Rixer arriving too, opening a small part of the shields to let the Maximal through. He then sends a comm to Iron Raptor.

"Commander, I think you've noticed, but there's a ship right above us. What do you want me to do?"
